data.description: SELLERS WILL CONTRIBUTE UP TO $10,000 TOWARDS BUYERS' CLOSING COSTS!! Lovely Craftsman Bungalow on a corner lot! Built in 1945 and remodeled just a few years ago. Charming and easy care 2 Bedrooms-1 Bath home, includes a spacious living room, large kitchen area with granite countertops, good sized bedrooms, separate eating area and laundry space, washer and dryer stays! New vinyl plank flooring recently installed. Very clean and move in ready! This home has ample parking and a large fenced front yard. Nice garden area could be expanded for flowers or vegetables! Don't miss out on all the wonderful aspects of this home! Close to transit, shopping and Navy Shipyard!
